Hedonometer,is,a,service,for,measuring,the,happiness,of,large,populations,in,real,time,using,social,media,Its,primary,data,source,is,currently,Twitter,although,this,could,be,expanded,in,the,future,The,Hedonometer,API,allows,researchers,and,developers,to,programmatically,retrieve,data,from,Hedonometer,Data,taken,from,Twitter,is,updated,on,a,daily,basis